{
  "stem": "20711.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So from the outside, nobody knew there it is a hole under the barrow.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I had no electricity, naturally, but I was given candles.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was also told try not to use the candle too much, because it takes oxygen.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they was not sure how much oxygen is going to be used and how much is going to be needed or how long I'm going to be there.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they were concerned of that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they said to try to keep it to the minimum.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there was just a bucket for the waste.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And once a day, there would be another bucket coming down with food.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they would-- I would put my bucket on that hook, and they would take it away.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they would do that first thing in the morning before-- because usually, the bombing happened during the night and very rarely during the day.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it was a terrible experience.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was there for, for eternity.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It looked the longest period of my life.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I had nothing to do.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I couldn't read.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I had absolutely nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I was cold, damp, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] and the most scariest part was when, during the bombing, I heard the people above me crying and praying and be afraid.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I didn't have anybody to cry to or being comforted.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Those people were comforted with each other, and I had to be alone.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I was afraid if something happened to the bomb shelter, maybe a bomb will hit them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Maybe my uncle will die, too, and nobody will ever know I am down here.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Nobody knew beside him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So his life was as important as mine, because if he dies, I'm gone.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And it was a very scary experience.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
